snippet.title: Note Ban: Long Queues Return outside Banks and ATMs

localized.description:
Note ban: Long queues return outside banks. Peoples are standing in queues outside ATMs and banks to withdraw cash from their bank accounts. Opposition parties like Congress, TMC, AAP are continuously attacking Modi government in the Parliament over demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes.
